{"tid":1459840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有本身呢幾日會飛既人入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-12T22:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T03:08:26.000Z","uid":294513,"like":21,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0375904d235e21994ba6333abffc3221c8cf5740","tid":1459840,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T22:43:14.000Z","msg":"眼見好多人話為左香港⋯⋯飛唔到蝕左機票酒店錢等等都冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地當份旅遊保廢架？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔知claim唔claim到或者唔識claim或者有問題想問既全部放低你地既問題，我會盡快回覆</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>連登咁多保險佬，係時候做野幫下啲學生喇屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Claim撚爆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />買左保險就緊係要用架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"db69e2b9252cac3131f5fa34b044bce2c3922996","tid":1459840,"uid":189109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T22:44:58.000Z","msg":"不如你直接講點樣CLAIM好過啦"},{"pid":"1a5b11e917d6e6559a0d5f5908615d22aaf81cc2","tid":1459840,"uid":294513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"db69e2b9252cac3131f5fa34b044bce2c3922996","tid":1459840,"uid":189109,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T22:44:58.000Z","msg":"不如你直接講點樣CLAIM好過啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T22:52:22.000Z","msg":"你岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>保留所有機票、登記證、已經落左訂既收據（酒店、Local Tour等等），呢幾樣野係基本必需品！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n其他情況例如上限賠到幾錢等等每間公司都會有出入<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>格式提供<br />\n買左邊間公司：<br />\n咩plan：<br />\n想問啲咩：</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"5b0b05ce0424ccaf6031b21ea50f85ff72cfcb5f","tid":1459840,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T22:53:55.000Z","msg":"希望幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 輕輕一推"},{"pid":"513060dc8969524ffc99a26c4636339a414e0001","tid":1459840,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:01:41.000Z","msg":"612721811"},{"pid":"890949b7292af8d1a1596f12005335e7c867a764","tid":1459840,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eebfa1527c15794c15444f6d4157939c573714af","tid":1459840,"uid":39880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:12:35.000Z","msg":"Separate onward逼住要改埋有無得賠"},{"pid":"b7fbe209adbf3984738cf81faafa87a1936dff19","tid":1459840,"uid":39880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eebfa1527c15794c15444f6d4157939c573714af","tid":1459840,"uid":39880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:12:35.000Z","msg":"Separate onward逼住要改埋有無得賠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:14:03.000Z","msg":"買左Chubb 金計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc32c9153d9ee6b42d48ada3090041d7d722d88f","tid":1459840,"uid":63311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:14:32.000Z","msg":"保險佬同我入黎"},{"pid":"d4c341b0659b7a24ab8ed8b1b4272a1e61e21cd2","tid":1459840,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"eebfa1527c15794c15444f6d4157939c573714af","tid":1459840,"uid":39880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:12:35.000Z","msg":"Separate onward逼住要改埋有無得賠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:19:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />⋯⋯⋯對唔住，我認我讀唔成書先走去做保險，我係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可唔可以用返中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我係文盲<br />\n我係垃圾<br />\n我係廢物<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bab0b7f381f731e598881d91611dcb19fd59b563","tid":1459840,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eebfa1527c15794c15444f6d4157939c573714af","tid":1459840,"uid":39880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:12:35.000Z","msg":"Separate onward逼住要改埋有無得賠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:30:21.000Z","msg":"根據偉大既google大神翻譯下我估大約係想問分開出發但迫住要改行程有冇得賠係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d089ef54548cf4d111a45dc8e4faf8d4b2a09454","tid":1459840,"uid":109862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:41:17.000Z","msg":"航班取消邊間有得賠？"},{"pid":"671ea8bd705646b041987a8333845677196850a0","tid":1459840,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eebfa1527c15794c15444f6d4157939c573714af","tid":1459840,"uid":39880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:12:35.000Z","msg":"Separate onward逼住要改埋有無得賠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:41:52.000Z","msg":"如果係既話<br />\n答案係有得賠<br />\n例如假如因為航班取消或延誤，導致到你原本book左而且比左訂金既任何行程（如Local Tour、演唱會門票、遊樂場門票等等）去唔成被迫取消，相關費用一律可以Claim得返，保留返<span style=\"color: red;\">落訂收據(online版本都得）、機票及登機證、由航空公司發出之取消航班或航班延誤之證明(試過就咁email都做到證明)</span>，將以上文件填好後寄比保險公司就冇問題。<br />\n<br />\nChubb旅遊保賠償連結 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chubbtravelinsurance.com.hk/zh/claim\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chubbtravelinsurance.com.hk%2Fzh%2Fclaim&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=c3f9cb87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chubbtravelinsurance.com.hk/zh/claim</a><br />\n<br />\n下載並且列印呢份Claim Form<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chubbtravelinsurance.com.hk/aceStatic/Doc/HK/ClaimForm.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chubbtravelinsurance.com.hk%2FaceStatic%2FDoc%2FHK%2FClaimForm.pdf&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=069d224b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chubbtravelinsurance.com.hk/aceStatic/Doc/HK/ClaimForm.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n填好後e-mail send去<br />\nA&amp;<a href=\"http://HClaims.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHClaims.HK&d=9IUie9AXCQLlCDjKIEsB2%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=99967ce7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">HClaims.HK</a>@chubb.com<br />\n<br />\n記得留份CC比自己"},{"pid":"48f1e5b82eeb7d00c44ab33dd64c79705c6fa593","tid":1459840,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d089ef54548cf4d111a45dc8e4faf8d4b2a09454","tid":1459840,"uid":109862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:41:17.000Z","msg":"航班取消邊間有得賠？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:44:29.000Z","msg":"基本上間間都有得賠，差別在於<span style=\"color: red;\">賠到幾多</span><br />\n<br />\n多數每間公司既旅遊保都會有2-3種plan比你簡，愈貴既plan保障額會愈高"},{"pid":"56b747773be7affe58d61e0a1934c39dd5ea418c","tid":1459840,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d089ef54548cf4d111a45dc8e4faf8d4b2a09454","tid":1459840,"uid":109862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:41:17.000Z","msg":"航班取消邊間有得賠？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:46:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">留意</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家先買旅保既話好大幾會唔包，因為保險唔會包係你買之前已經發生緊既事，買之前最好打去問清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"f5f96edcf65b98d02bbc32f04c0459aeb97697ac","tid":1459840,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:49:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">612<br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港     時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">推一推先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"ab6bb73ad5d1c20dee5a377ce65e2eabb08caa77","tid":1459840,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6933e567221f42ae14a39ab338dbd32094ecd472","tid":1459840,"uid":39880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bab0b7f381f731e598881d91611dcb19fd59b563","tid":1459840,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eebfa1527c15794c15444f6d4157939c573714af","tid":1459840,"uid":39880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:12:35.000Z","msg":"Separate onward逼住要改埋有無得賠"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T23:30:21.000Z","msg":"根據偉大既google大神翻譯下我估大約係想問分開出發但迫住要改行程有冇得賠係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:24:50.000Z","msg":"係有張香港去A<br />\n再由A去B咁<br />\n其實係要去B<br />\n呢兩張飛就分開買既⋯<br />\n兩間唔同航空公司<br />\n<br />\nAnyway thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f8df13b82f503044886fa72ca9fdd5b603223e","tid":1459840,"uid":257351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:44:21.000Z","msg":"歐盟有條Rule係Flight Cancel/Delay 係Eligible for claiming EUR600 per person <br />\n大家去呢個Website 睇下合唔合資格 但如果成功佢會收返25% Commission <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://app.airhelp.com/claims/new/trip-details?_gl=1*17ld7qb*_ga*YW1wLXZETk1rVUVNZ0NCZVFDSWpYSU9PenRHN3JVbTcxaEZJUmhubGhXZnJLVGYwZkQyZmszN3JkZnpnN1FFTHFMNUs.\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp.airhelp.com%2Fclaims%2Fn