ts/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T00:24:50.000Z","msg":"係有張香港去A<br />\n再由A去B咁<br />\n其實係要去B<br />\n呢兩張飛就分開買既⋯<br />\n兩間唔同航空公司<br />\n<br />\nAnyway thanks<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:12:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌所以你話讀書係幾咁重要<br />\n<br />\nBtw在於保險黎講係冇影響<br />\n保險公司唔會理你去邊，只要你係香港出發+回程係香港就得<br />\n<br />\n例如如果你由香港飛去目的地A，但因為航班延誤或取消嘅原因導致到你趕唔切搭飛機去目的地B，呢個時候一樣有得賠"},{"pid":"44b7fde3b9f0814103299cdf0891cd642675b749","tid":1459840,"uid":294513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a713fe71740fb0808bbef35fd7bc775e23765b75","tid":1459840,"uid":188477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:10:11.000Z","msg":"係咪月底飛都冇得賠？<br />\n<br />\n保誠話如果都係因為依個事件發生引致都冇得賠"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:15:28.000Z","msg":"睇你幾時買呢份旅遊保<br />\n如果係事件發生前買就唔洗驚，照賠<br />\n但如果今日先買就唔得<br />\n因為保護公司<span style=\"color: red;\">正常情況下係唔會保埋已經發生左既事</span><br />\n旅遊保愈早買係愈著數"},{"pid":"d793e91ac68c21afbdc106a234bfd0735e1fb605","tid":1459840,"uid":294513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T06:18:13.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}